42 1.03.42.42 0 .78-.14 1.06-.42l1.23-1.25.79-.78 1.15-1.16c.08-.09.19-.22.28-.4.1-.2.15-.42.15-.67 0-.16-.02-.3-.06-.45l-.02-.02v-.02l-.07-.14s0-.03-.04-.06l-.06-.13-.02-.02c0-.02 0-.03-.02-.05a.6.6 0 0 0-.14-.16l-.48-.5c0-.04.02-.1.04-.15l.06-.12 1.17-1.14.09-.09.56.57c.02.04.08.1.16.18l.05.04.03.06.04.05.03.04.04.06.1.14.02.02c0 .02.01.03.03.04l.1.2v.02c.1.16.2.38.3.68a1 1 0 0 1 .04.25 3.2 3.2 0 0 1 .02 1.33 3.49 3.49 0 0 1-.95 1.87l-.66.67-.97.97-1.56 1.57a3.4 3.4 0 0 1-2.47 1.02c-.97 0-1.8-.34-2.49-1.03l-1.3-1.3a3.55 3.55 0 0 1-1-2.51v-.01h-.02v.02zm5.39-3.43c0-.19.02-.4.07-.63.13-.74.44-1.37.95-1.87l.66-.67.97-.98 1.56-1.56c.68-.69 1.5-1.03 2.47-1.03.97 0 1.8.34 2.48 1.02l1.3 1.32a3.48 3.48 0 0 1 1 2.48c0 .58-.11 1.11-.37 1.6l-.02.02v.02l-.02.04c-.14.27-.35.54-.6.8L16.23 15l-.01.02-.01.02c-.44.42-.92.7-1.43.83a4.55 4.55 0 0 0 1.23-3.52L18 10.38c.18-.21.3-.42.35-.65a2.03 2.03 0 0 0-.01-.9 1.96 1.96 0 0 0-.36-.58l-1.3-1.3a1.49 1.49 0 0 0-1.06-.42c-.42 0-.77.14-1.06.4l-1.2 1.27-.8.8-1.16 1.15c-.08.08-.18.21-.29.4a1.66 1.66 0 0 0-.08 1.12l.02.03v.02l.06.14s.01.03.05.06l.06.13.02.02.01.02.01.02c.05.08.1.13.14.16l.47.5c0 .04-.02.09-.04.15l-.06.12-1.15 1.15-.1.08-.56-.56a2.3 2.3 0 0 0-.18-.19c-.02-.01-.02-.03-.02-.04l-.02-.02a.37.37 0 0 1-.1-.12c-.03-.03-.05-.04-.05-.06l-.1-.15-.02-.02-.02-.04-.08-.17v-.02a5.1 5.1 0 0 1-.28-.69 1.03 1.03 0 0 1-.04-.26c-.06-.23-.1-.46-.1-.7v.01z" fill="#A8A8A8"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="bk l"><div><div class="bj" aria-hidden="false"></div></div></div></div></header><span class="l"></span><section><div><div class="dr gu gv gw gx gy"></div><div class="gz ha hb hc hd"><div class=""><h1 id="8725" class="pw-post-title he hf hg bc hh hi hj hk hl hm hn ho hp hq hr hs ht hu hv hw hx hy hz ia ib ic bh">Galactic Regulations of Space Station Docking in Star Atlas</h1></div><p id="18d6" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh"><em class="jb">“Secure your seat, save your feet, docking safety can’t be beat!”</em></p><p id="f01c" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh">The developing <a class="jc jd gc" href="https://medium.com/u/5ed69ff9cfb0?source=post_page-----9651b51a0695--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a> world is a unique and immersive <strong class="if hh">metaverse</strong> experience that combines the elements of gaming, space exploration, and cryptocurrency. While the game itself is already becoming a captivating experience, it’s important for any new or veteran pilot to<strong class="if hh"> review these important</strong> <strong class="if hh">precautions while</strong> <strong class="if hh">docking or undocking to Galactic Space Stations</strong>.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fb jj ep eq paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl dh jm be jn"><div class="ep eq je"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.webp 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*vs_fCJXuvlkDdVWmyVqQxw.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="NotBitcoinCEO Space Station" class="be jo jp c" width="700" height="476" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div></figure><h2 id="adb8" class="jq jr hg bc js jt ju jv jw jx jy jz ka io kb kc kd is ke kf kg iw kh ki kj kk bh">Space Stations Can Be a Tricky Place for a New Pilot</h2><p id="c5d1" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig kl ii ij ik km im in io kn iq ir is ko iu iv iw kp iy iz ja gz bh">Since the Treaty of Peace was established by the Galactic Council, space travel has become an exciting and rapidly advancing field, offering<strong class="if hh"> new opportunities for exploration and discovery</strong>. However, with this progress comes the need for increased safety measures. <strong class="if hh">Docking and undocking procedures</strong>, in particular, are critical moments during space travel that require the utmost attention and care. Protocols and procedures must be followed to ensure the safety of all crew members and passengers. <strong class="if hh">Here are ten safety protocols to keep in mind:</strong></p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fb jj ep eq paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl dh jm be jn"><div class="ep eq kq"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.webp 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*kFJwongHgj02xW5K.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="NotBitcoinCEO Space Seats" class="be jo jp c" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></figure><ol class=""><li id="a305" class="kr ks hg if b ig ih ik il io kt is ku iw kv ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Stay seated</strong>. As a primary safety measure, all individuals on board are required to be seated and properly secured during any sudden changes in velocity. This includes both embarking and disembarking. It’s acknowledged that extended space travel will consist of long moments of relaxation among crew members. Activities, such as resting in a bed, enjoying time in the crew quarters, or providing maintenance on ship mechanics, must take a backseat when approaching or leaving Space Stations. The importance of adhering to proper docking protocols cannot be emphasized enough.</li><li id="10c6" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Inspections/Repairs. </strong>Before undocking, inspecting the spacecraft for damages or malfunctioning equipment may prove a useful tool before embarking on long adventures to distant locations.</li><li id="abd4" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Enable Q-LINK</strong>. Initiating the Quantum Entanglement Link is vital in meeting Galactic regulations and docking without fines. In most space stations, a quantum entanglement link must be established between ship and station, allowing for instant communication and navigation.</li><li id="365a" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Disengage Energy Shields. </strong>This is a requirement for all pilots in order to allow for proper docking procedures to take place within protocol distance. Space Stations are regularly enforced and don’t hold the same dangers as Deep Space.</li><li id="50c8" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Synchronize Time Dilation Field.</strong> Synchronizing with Space Stations will help avoid many temporal discrepancies during the docking process. While collisions are an unlikely occurrence, this simple step greatly reduces miscommunication between different technologies. Most ships will automatically do this for you, however it’s good to be aware of.</li><li id="84cb" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Activate Teleportation Systems</strong>. While normally automatic, many Space Stations in <em class="jb">The Outskirt Regions</em> maintain <em class="jb">power-efficient teleportation</em> that <em class="jb">must be powered on once docked</em>. The pilot may need to activate these systems after docking if they haven’t been automatically configured.</li><li id="9624" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Pressurization</strong>. Equalizing the pressure between the spacecraft and the space station is key in preventing damage to docking equipment or injury to the crew. When pressure systems have malfunctioned, do not open the hatch under any circumstances until help has arrived.</li><li id="fd6a" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Decontamination.</strong> Some space stations or colonies may require decontamination in order to gain entry. These are done in order to prevent the spread of contaminants in closed systems. This could possibly involve going through an <em class="jb">airlock</em> <em class="jb">or some other form of decontamination procedure</em>.</li><li id="c0fe" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Open Hangar Doors</strong>. Depending on what station you’re at, clearing the spacecraft for departure by verifying hangar doors are open<em class="jb"> before</em> liftoff<em class="jb"> </em>is vital.</li><li id="853c" class="kr ks hg if b ig la ik lb io lc is ld iw le ja kw kx ky kz bh"><strong class="if hh">Side-Docking Precautions. </strong>Pilots with side-docking capabilities should slowly pull into any given station aligning themselves with the received coordinates. Magnetic docking clamps will automatically attach to your ship as soon as your alignment parameters are correctly set up. Only until attachment is complete is it safe for the crew to maneuver around the ship and for the doors to be opened.</li></ol><figure class="jf jg jh ji fb jj ep eq paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl dh jm be jn"><div class="ep eq kq"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.webp 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*AHYuIR3fbUsAJ-gE.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="NotBitcoinCEO Space Friends" class="be jo jp c" width="700" height="700" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></figure><p id="f43d" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh">In conclusion, proper adherence to docking safety protocols is essential for the well-being of all individuals on board. Crew members must prioritize their safety by being seated and properly secured during all docking events. By following these protocols, we can improve the safety of all Galactic Citizens and avoid serious injury or death. <strong class="if hh">Failure to adhere to these protocols may result in revocation of station privilege.</strong></p><p id="5fe7" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh"><em class="jb">**This document is theoretical and is intended for safety purposes only.**</em></p><p id="52cc" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh">Would you like to check out <strong class="if hh">Star Atlas </strong>for yourself? <a class="ad lf" href="https://play.staratlas.com/?oid=3&amp;affid=253" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Join today</a>! Also, if you enjoyed this article or would like to hear about something specific in the future, <em class="jb">please leave a comment below</em>.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fb jj ep eq paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl dh jm be jn"><div class="ep eq lg"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.webp 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*Mk8sSW1jBVD5F69uDWOf6A.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="NotBitcoinCEO Space Motorcycle" class="be jo jp c" width="700" height="331" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></figure><h1 id="6ed0" class="lh jr hg bc js li lj lk jw ll lm ln ka lo lp lq kd lr ls lt kg lu lv lw kj lx bh">About the Author</h1><p id="1884" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig kl ii ij ik km im in io kn iq ir is ko iu iv iw kp iy iz ja gz bh"><a class="ad lf" rel="noopener" href="/@mudpilot"><strong class="if hh">NotBitcoinCEO</strong></a> is a mud pilot &amp; writer on The Hologram News Network, an independent blockchain gaming meta-news organization devoted to the coverage of Star Atlas.</p><p id="09e2" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh">Follow on Social Media:</p><p id="901d" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh"><a class="ad lf" href="https://twitter.com/Hologram_News" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Twitter</a> | <a class="ad lf" href="https://www.instagram.com/hologram_news/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Instagram</a> | <a class="ad lf" href="https://thehologram.io/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Web</a></p><h1 id="aae4" class="lh jr hg bc js li lj lk jw ll lm ln ka lo lp lq kd lr ls lt kg lu lv lw kj lx bh">About The Hologram</h1><p id="c00e" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig kl ii ij ik km im in io kn iq ir is ko iu iv iw kp iy iz ja gz bh"><a class="ad lf" href="https://medium.com/the-hologram" rel="noopener">The Hologram</a> is Star Atlas’ first and only independent news network. Our vision is to become the most trusted source of information about Star Atlas and a voice for the whole community. Readers can expect a high standard from our reporting and staff. Our promise to you: we will not publish anything that hasn’t been thoroughly researched and based on the best facts available.</p><figure class="jf jg jh ji fb jj ep eq paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jk jl dh jm be jn"><div class="ep eq ly"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.webp 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*i9Q0zOxjxBPA_-9n.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="NotBitcoinCEO — The Hologram" class="be jo jp c" width="700" height="200" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></figure><p id="d0d1" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hg if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja gz bh">The Hologram is not endorsed or paid by the <a class="ad lf" href="https://staratlas.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a> team. Any information published by The Hologram nor its writers should be considered as informational in nature and does not constitute any financial advice.</p></div></div></section></div></div></article></div></div></div><div class="z ck"><div class="dj be dk dl dm dn"><div class="lz ma z gd"><div class="mb z"><a class="mc av ak md" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/star-atlas?source=post_page-----9651b51a0695---------------star_atlas-----------------"><div class="me dh ds mf mg mh bc b bd y bh mi">Star Atlas</div></a></div><div class="mb z"><a class="mc av ak md" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/scifi?source=post_page-----9651b51a0695---------------scifi-----------------"><div class="me dh ds mf mg mh bc b bd y bh mi">Sci Fi</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="l"></div><footer class="mj mk ml mm mn mo mp mq mr z q ms mt c"><div class="l ac"><div class="z ck"><div class="dj be dk dl dm dn"><div class="z fd mu"><div class="z q ca"><div class="mv l"><span class="l fk mw mx e d"><div class="z q ca"><div class="pw-multi-vote-icon dh my mz na nb"><div class=""><div class="nc nd ne nf ng nh ni ak nj nk nl nb"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="clap"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11.37.83L12 3.28l.63-2.45h-1.26zM15.42 1.84